  <p class="pt-3">Your PayPal account is already integrated with YAVOLO. Do you want to <a data-paypal-button="true" href="<%=@action_url%>&displayMode=minibrowser" class="btn btn-outline-primary" target="PPFrame">Update</a> PayPal Integration?</p>
  </div>
